Vote for that property and based on the form a the property was voted to be historically significant.

16
00:01:21,005 --> 00:01:26,247
And to remind folks what that means to be considered historically significant.

17
00:01:26,848 --> 00:01:31,910
It means that the commission felt the property was importantly associated with one or more historic.

18
00:01:32,530 --> 00:01:55,704
persons or events, or with the broad architectural, cultural, political, economic, or social history of the city or the Commonwealth, or that it is historically or architecturally important in terms of period, style, method of building construction, or association with an important architect or builder, either by itself or in the context of a group of buildings.

19
00:01:56,504 --> 00:02:02,793
So as I mentioned last month to to to Boston have was voted historically significant based on that criteria.

20
00:02:03,695 --> 00:02:10,985
