236
00:20:09,512 --> 00:20:17,977
If a property is importantly associated with one or more historic persons or events, or with the broad architectural, cultural, political, economic,

237
00:20:18,397 --> 00:20:33,404
or social history of the city or the Commonwealth, or that it is historically or architecturally important in terms of period, style, method of building construction, or association with an important architect or builder, either by itself or in the context of a group of buildings.

238
00:20:34,284 --> 00:20:36,825
So we did reach out to our consultant.

239
00:20:36,905 --> 00:20:40,067
We have form Bs tonight for all three properties.

